  "body": "Currently, to scaffold a new contract users need to run THREE separate commands!\r\n\r\n```\r\ntruffle create contract foo\r\ntruffle create migration foo\r\ntruffle create test foo\r\n```\r\n\r\nDo you think we have robot fingers or something?? 😅\r\n\r\nMy argument is that there is ***NEVER*** a good time to create a contract _without_ a migration file or a test file...\r\n\r\nTherefore, all three of these files should be created from the `truffle create contract` command...",
